n`、`amount > 0` 后，对该用户执行 `ZINCRBY leaderboard:103 uid amount`。\n   111
\t- **战功榜**：收到 `COMBAT_KILL` 后，对该用户执行 `ZINCRBY leaderboard:104 uid
